'''Janet''' came into the [[Mayo Clinic]] with a PDA and a heart blockage.

==History==
Janet was diagnosed with a PDA and then with heart blockage. The original plan was for them to fix them both in a single surgery, first repairing the PDA from the side and then opening up the blockage from the front. However, when Cristina pressured him, he changed his surgical plan to a hybrid surgery.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married to [[Jeff]].
